	dprr:hasNoteText "On Metilius' tribunate, see Niccolini, FTP 90f.; and under 217, when a Metilius held this office. Münzer suggests that he held two tribunates, one with Flaminius as Censor and one with him as Consul (RE, no. 9)." .
